{"id": "1215245607774461972", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "某種意義上融災是新的平衡環境，某些角色如果缺少登場機會會補強的。", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:32:11.065000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1184375279389515849"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1215193060690886686", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215246318021120070", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "很抱歉團隊在忙於製作新喚醒體以及相關新活動，顯然幻夢深潛滿分難度評估存在嚴重不足。", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:35:00.401000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215247249131446272", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我們會在下週更新中對積分部分作出調整，也包括新的特殊難度，不增加融蝕之珠獎勵，使之適合大多數人，同時提供額外積分倍率，但怪物等級更高，也有融災黑潮，黑印死亡抵抗計分上限也會翻倍。這個積分模式中當存在滿分就意味著大家有更高的潛力，需要想辦法擴展才能區分。", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:38:42.395000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215247375145238558", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "也會繼續增加一次性積分成就獎勵。", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:39:12.439000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215251141294817330", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "~~意味著大家都裝滿死抗命輪存錢不買造物打遊戲~~", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T10:54:10.359000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215267518302916688", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 19, "author_id": "726748815058665574", "author_name": "shinjyo1st", "author_bot": false, "content": "不覺得是記分方向的錯誤嗎? 原來區別玩家能力的方式只剩死抗跟黑印", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T11:59:14.942000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫠", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1215247249131446272", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215268712547090492", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "771169877121564703", "author_name": "yang_42", "author_bot": false, "content": "除了死抗黑印好像也没多少东西好记分了", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T12:03:59.672000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215268811553636363", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "726748815058665574", "author_name": "shinjyo1st", "author_bot": false, "content": "黑印在提高一倍 真的是不要買東西了", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T12:04:23.277000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215271923466899487", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "726748815058665574", "author_name": "shinjyo1st", "author_bot": false, "content": "以後直接抄滿分的隊伍就好 反正都不能買 也不存在甚麼造物刻印搭配問題了 懂抄就行", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T12:16:45.215000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215278856324517920", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "726748815058665574", "author_name": "shinjyo1st", "author_bot": false, "content": "說實話不想讓人滿分 把血量加回來就好了...今天滿分的人很多都沒滿血吧...如果覺得血量計分對某些隊伍不友善 把上限調成50%血量或是更低 這樣也有承傷的空間\n限制黑印讓大家不要買東西 做出跟整個遊戲玩法背道而馳的模式真的很沒必要", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T12:44:18.137000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215299239177879572", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "699270788578148442", "author_name": "_buqi", "author_bot": false, "content": "我覺得可以搞個特殊詞條，\n供玩家選擇 再依詞條增設評分\n例如保護校貓：開始時校貓跟在身邊 \n單次受到一定傷害 校貓血量減少，最後依校貓血量 增加分數\n造物刻印侵蝕：勾選後本場戰鬥所獲得的部分造物刻印  其本身的數值降低", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T14:05:17.788000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215332224665133117", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "386730481502257153", "author_name": "yulina_aa", "author_bot": false, "content": "融災黑潮真的很不好玩", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T16:16:22.141000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215332329686310993", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "386730481502257153", "author_name": "yulina_aa", "author_bot": false, "content": "不要甚麼高難都塞這個好不好", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T16:16:47.180000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215341834734149672", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "392840163732226058", "author_name": "vegoutdino", "author_bot": false, "content": "有沒有考慮給菲茵特一些特權?", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T16:54:33.360000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1215372954142117898", "channel_id": "1212267053570850826", "type": 0, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@633215996508766229>  \n  關於黑潮和幻夢 ：我建議幻夢分數條件可以改成讓玩家自選 不管是黑印數量 死扛結餘 或是增加怪物的傷害 血量 削減玩家防禦 生命等 讓玩家能自主性的去決定自己的陣容方向 以達到更高的分數 而不是用一個簡單方便的黑潮 去打壓各隊伍的強度 你們是方便了 但讓玩家玩的很不舒服 \n\n如果把選擇權交到玩家手上 至少可玩性會高上不少 想摸索的玩家也有很大的空間能去玩 以玩家心理 能自主決定也會更容易接受\n\n黑潮的存在也相當荒謬 只是在告知玩家你們無力平衡 所以只要強的隊伍 我就在黑潮這個限制器上限制你 你們是輕鬆方便了 但遊戲性呢？\n隊伍的強處都被砍了 玩個遊戲都不快樂了 原本熟悉的玩法 盾擊疊不了盾 毒爆疊不了毒 爆發打不死王 狂氣輪轉也轉不起來了 那玩家剩下什麼 要玩什麼 你們原本設定的隊伍強項都被抹除了 在你們額外給定的限制條件下苦苦求存 玩家是來玩遊戲還是來坐牢的？\n\n幻夢的建議應該能滿足你們不想要成為一款爽遊 也能讓玩家有決策權 思考如何達到更高分的目的", "timestamp": "2024-03-07T18:58:12.805000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-07T18:58:35.372000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1212267053570850826", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「幻夢深潛」的調整計劃", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
